@@ @@
+++ Human history was [[span]]the continued fight[[/span]] [[span]] against an endless threat.[[/span]]
+++ It has tormented us, [[span]]crushed us,[[/span]] [[span]]and devastated us.[[/span]]
+++ However, [[span class="divide"]][[span]]the very new step[[/span]] [[span]]after all of them,[[/span]][[/span]] [[span]]is what we truly are.[[/span]]
@@ @@
+++ You devoted yourself to it [[span class="divide"]][[span]]at the forefront[[/span]] [[span]]of the Foundation duty.[[/span]][[/span]]
+++ We are all in debt [[span]]of your intense commitment.[[/span]]
+++ To praise your huge contribution [[span class="divide"]][[span]]to protect humanity[[/span]] [[span]]and the normalcy,[[/span]][[/span]]
+++ On behalf of the [[span]]entire human race,[[/span]] [[span]]we will remember your honor.[[/span]]
